# FTGO Monolith - Code Owners
#
# This file defines code ownership for the FTGO monolith and
# microservices migration project. Code owners are automatically
# requested for review when a pull request modifies files they own.
#
# Ownership follows the microservices migration team structure.
# Each service team owns their extracted service code and the
# corresponding monolith module.
#
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ============================================
# Default Owners (fallback for all files)
# ============================================
* @COG-GTM/ftgo-maintainers

